components.description: Loads and validates the aggregated sales CSV files produced by the upstream DAG.

connections.purpose: Access aggregated CSV files and store validated data

components.name: Generate Executive Dashboard
components.description: Creates an executive dashboard with sales metrics, visualizations, and regional analysis from the validated sales data.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the sales CSV has been successfully loaded and validated.

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

timeout.description: Maximum time (seconds) to wait for the external DAG
